headline: Hershey joins food makers in commitment to remove artificial dyes
summary: The Jolly Rancher and Twizzlers maker joins a fast-growing list of companies making similar pledges amid mounting pressure from states and the Trump administration.

headline: S&P 500 Rallies 5% In June To Close Month At Record High
summary: The S&P 500 extended its now two-and-a-half-month rally through June to end the month at a record high.
